{"tid":1721013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中原地產紅磡舖遭破壞 6月以來第4間店被「裝修」","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:20:41.000Z","uid":236171,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"39fcf4cdf38659bebb516b69f6d194cb81fbcc79","tid":1721013,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:07:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【修例風波 】中原地產紅磡舖遭破壞 6月以來第4間店被「裝修」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fSQVFKS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfSQVFKS.gif&h=df2cb5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反修例風波持續5個多月，社會局勢欠明朗，部份店舖亦受破壞，包括從事地產買賣租賃代理的分行，亦不能幸免。<br />\n<br />\n市場流傳一段片段，位於紅磡黃埔德民街的中原地產地舖，昨夜遭到黑衣示威者肆意破壞，暫時未知原因。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者今日到現場直擊該舖，遭破壞的中原地產分行，位於黃埔德民街60D地舖，現場所見，該地舖現已封上白色圍板，有員工下午到場開門收拾物品。店舖內滿目瘡痍，環境一片凌亂，連天花板的光管都被拆下。同一條街上，只有該中原地產店舖及中移動遭「裝修」，鄰近的三間地產舖則沒有任何損壞，照常營業。至於，同屬黃埔區的中原地產店舖，位於德民街以及船澳街的兩間地舖，則沒有受破壞，今日照常營業，舖內亦有員工正在工作。<br />\n<br />\n網上有傳，該舖一名女員工日前向一名舉示威文宣的女學生影大頭照，及後報警令女生被捕。就中原地產有店舖被「裝修」，本報向中原集團查詢，該公司發言人稱暫不作回應。據消息指，自6月修例風波後，中原地產在港至少有4間分行被破壞，包括位於馬鞍山、上水、天水圍及紅磡。"},{"pid":"a02c88d5b4463ce73e97229260e5ae6e4d578611","tid":1721013,"uid":102700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:08:03.000Z","msg":"利嘉閣都係屍永青"},{"pid":"52d902123e8bee649cfbccf73630bf87d8a81f62","tid":1721013,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f8177b6abb2c5c59f2bb1b69947ed2c56f3a155","tid":1721013,"uid":68598,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:08:13.000Z","msg":"該舖一名女員工日前向一名舉示威文宣的女學生影大頭照，及後報警令女生被捕。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做得好 dklm"},{"pid":"dd6c69fc4358d63d7baa85fb4d94973e50f11c55","tid":1721013,"uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pX6YDxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpX6YDxu.png&h=51b8c239&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84b2ddf0e943e08230ef168ee7cd132dd1089041","tid":1721013,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"準備下個月寄聖誕卡比屍永青"},{"pid":"b5898fa08e25e014d8ec288661449054449bba3e","tid":1721013,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84b2ddf0e943e08230ef168ee7cd132dd1089041","tid":1721013,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"準備下個月寄聖誕卡比屍永青"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"一人一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8bc03353184c9f4d37b63d7611baaf44d8b841","tid":1721013,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個累全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b29b90931343ed04d45d302f91d1b43ac3da18","tid":1721013,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">該舖一名女員工日前向一名舉示威文宣的女學生影大頭照，及後報警令女生被捕。</span></span>"},{"pid":"f219c3bfdc5ff8eb61246eb4ea313bbd9fc4dcb9","tid":1721013,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:11:51.000Z","msg":"【被擄走女孩訪問】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720852</a>"},{"pid":"c5a